oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: C. V. Warren Job No. 38641
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Hitchcock, Stan;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 3160) for an order placed for the Shiloh Dude Ranch by C. V. Warren for 100 two color jumbos for the Country Music Talent Contest and Stan Hitchcock at the Shiloh Dude Ranch on July 24. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
